    Scope and Contents
Post discusses her father and his business, the Postum Cereal Company, from its beginnings, her family, early life, travels; her father's inventions, life, and philosophies; and Midwest life in the early 20th century.Memoir, 37 pp.
Interview by John T. Mason, Jr., 1964
